<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Turtle Shelter</title>
    <!-- 
        Company Colors:
        Main: #35B3A8 
        Main Dark: #3D9991
        Lighter Gray: #333
        Darker Gray: #1F1F1F
    -->

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9fafc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .homeBtnDiv {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header {
            background: url('header-image.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            z-index: 2;
            position: relative;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            z-index: 2;
            position: relative;
        }

        header .btn {
            margin: 20px;
            z-index: 2;
            position: relative;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            background: #35B3A8;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #3D9991;
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .headerImg {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: top;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .containerHead {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header class="z-10">
        <img class="headerImg z-0"
            src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5b5a266fcef372310148d6d6/1567462206269-3U6NXPS9IWC1S97PD39J/Picture11.jpg?format=2500w"
            alt="Turtle Shelter Logo">
        <p class="z-10">Helping to save lives of people experiencing homelessness</p>
        <h1 class="font-bold z-10">STARTS WITH YOU</h1>
        <div id="homeBtnDiv">
            <a href="#learn-more" class="btn z-0">Learn More</a>
            <a href="#donate" class="btn z-0">Donate</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black">What is a Turtle Shelter Vest?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-3">
                A portable, high-tech solution designed to provide warmth and protection, just like a turtle’s shell. Simple, effective, and life-saving.
            </p>
            <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                <li class="flex items-center">Prevents hypothermia temperatures down to
                    <span class="font-semibold text-3xl m-2" style="color: #35B3A8;">-10&deg;F</span>.
                </li>
                <li>Keeps you warm even when wet.</li>
            </ul>            
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-6 text-center">
            <strong>YOU</strong> have the power to make a real difference!
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-row gap-4">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-between">
                    <div id="volunteerHead" class="containerHead">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl text-black">Take Action</h2>
                        <a href="volunteerRequest" class="btn w-fit">Volunteer →</a>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Ready to take the next step? You can become a volunteer so we can keep you updated on events
                        near you!
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-row gap-4">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-between">
                    <div id="volunteerHead" class="containerHead">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl text-black">Host an Event</h2>
                        <a href="/hostAnEvent" class="btn w-fit">Become a Host →</a>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        Hosting an event brings your community together and makes an impact. Organize a vest-making
                        workshop, fundraiser, or awareness campaign to support our mission and save lives.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>